        <title>ShokaX插件-移除頂部模糊效果</title>
        <link rel="alternate" href="https://blog.minz.li/shokaX/ShokaX%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6-%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E9%A0%82%E9%83%A8%E9%9C%A7%E9%9D%A2%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C/"/>
        <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-src=&#34;/assets/ShokaXPlugin/removeTopFrosted_before.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;移除前&#34; width=&#34;80%&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-src=&#34;/assets/ShokaXPlugin/removeTopFrosted_after.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;移除後&#34; width=&#34;80%&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;並且在頂部以外的地方保留模糊效果&lt;br /&gt;
